00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,820
My sister is digging bamboo shoots.

315
00:23:19,820 --> 00:23:21,879
 Just hang on, I'll give her the phone. 

316
00:23:21,879 --> 00:23:24,319
All right, thanks.

317
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:28,440
Who is it?

318
00:23:52,060 --> 00:23:53,560
Hello?

319
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:57,980
It's me. Yu Tu.

320
00:24:03,499 --> 00:24:05,199
Are you digging bamboo shoots?

321
00:24:05,939 --> 00:24:07,899
 Did you go to the mountains? 

322
00:24:10,219 --> 00:24:11,459
I was about to ask you

323
00:24:11,459 --> 00:24:14,520
if you cared to go on a stroll with me this afternoon.

324
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:17,210
Yixing has changed a lot in the past two years.

325
00:24:17,210 --> 00:24:19,560
The Dongjiu Lakeside is beautiful.

326
00:24:20,019 --> 00:24:22,499
I'm at my grandma's in Hufu.

327
00:24:22,499 --> 00:24:24,179
Tomorrow, I'll be at my grandpa's in the mountains.

328
00:24:24,179 --> 00:24:25,692
 I don't have time. 

329
00:24:27,259 --> 00:24:30,420
Okay then. Have fun.

330
00:24:33,019 --> 00:24:36,839
On the fourth day, I will take you back to Shanghai.

331
00:24:38,979 --> 00:24:42,040
We'll catch up then. Bye.

332
00:25:03,979 --> 00:25:05,579
Sister.

333
00:25:05,579 --> 00:25:08,620
As an actress, you even had to act when picking up the phone?

334
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:12,060
You already knew who called, yet you had to ask me about it.

335
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:14,240
You even made me answer it.

336
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:17,659
He persisted in calling so I had you pick it up instead.

337
00:25:17,659 --> 00:25:20,040
Couldn't you say I was not here?

338
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:21,400
Hurry up and dig.

339
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:23,100
I want fried winter bamboo shoots with pickles for dinner tonight.

340
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:25,599
Dig up! Stop fooling around.

341
00:25:27,380 --> 00:25:29,400
I think there are some here.

342
00:25:31,459 --> 00:25:33,559
You're the big sister. Anything you say.

343
00:25:41,599 --> 00:25:44,100
Mom, I'm going for a walk.

344
00:25:44,100 --> 00:25:46,179
- Where are you going? 
 - A scenic spot.

345
00:25:46,179 --> 00:25:48,520
Brother, I'm coming with you!

346
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:51,438
Get home early, okay?

347
00:25:53,699 --> 00:25:55,259
Whose turn is it?

348
00:25:55,259 --> 00:25:58,720
 The girl whose photo you posted, have you found her a boyfriend? 

349
00:25:58,720 --> 00:26:01,200
No, thanks.

350
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,780
Another six-dots.

351
00:26:03,780 --> 00:26:04,939
Make that two six-dots.

352
00:26:04,939 --> 00:26:07,939
 Not yet. I haven't even seen her mother lately. 

353
00:26:07,939 --> 00:26:09,580
 I haven't had time to tell you. 

354
00:26:09,580 --> 00:26:11,019
 Stop recommending her to others for now. 

355
00:26:11,019 --> 00:26:14,083
 Tomorrow night, you'll recommend her to Yu Tu over dinner. 

356
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:30,020
Brother, we've been walking all afternoon. Can we take a break?

357
00:26:30,020 --> 00:26:35,540
   

358
00:26:35,540 --> 00:26:38,280
It's already over 15,000 steps!

359
00:26:40,699 --> 00:26:41,939
That's it.

360
00:26:41,939 --> 00:26:43,903
I'm stopping here.

361
00:27:00,019 --> 00:27:01,380
If I knew it was like this,

362
00:27:01,380 --> 00:27:04,480
I might as well stay at home and chat with my girls.

363
00:27:05,427 --> 00:27:10,127
   

364
00:27:11,119 --> 00:27:13,480
But no one chats with me.

365
00:27:14,580 --> 00:27:17,700
How about I teach you a few tricks for tuition fee?

366
00:27:20,900 --> 00:27:22,400
Let's go home.

367
00:27:24,359 --> 00:27:26,769
Can't you even take a break?

368
00:27:27,319 --> 00:27:29,480
Wait for me!

369
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:35,380
We're on our way.

370
00:27:35,380 --> 00:27:38,497
We'll be in Taihua in about half an hour.

371
00:27:38,497 --> 00:27:40,779
Yes, we'll spend the night.

372
00:27:42,499 --> 00:27:44,979
Jingjing misses you too.

373
00:27:44,979 --> 00:27:46,800
Okay, bye.

374
00:28:33,740 --> 00:28:36,880
   

375
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:58,820
Surprised to see me, Grandma?

376
00:28:58,820 --> 00:29:02,359
My granddaughter's so big now!

377
00:29:02,879 --> 00:29:04,300
Did you sleep well?

378
00:29:04,300 --> 00:29:06,340
- All right, let's get us some breakfast. 
 - Sure.

379
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:09,019
- I made it just for you. 
 - Don't eat too much.

380
00:29:09,019 --> 00:29:11,739
Once your aunt gets here in a moment, we're starting the main meal.

381
00:29:11,739 --> 00:29:14,380
- Okay. 
 - I made you your favorites.

382
00:29:15,019 --> 00:29:16,220
That's enough, Grandma.

383
00:29:16,220 --> 00:29:19,510
Have some more. Ignore your mother and eat more.

384
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:23,960
My granddaughter loves zongzi so much.

385
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:26,300
Let me peel it for you.

386
00:29:26,320 --> 00:29:27,739
Careful, it's hot. 
    

387
00:29:27,739 --> 00:29:29,380
I'm fine. 
    

388
00:29:29,380 --> 00:29:31,580
This is your favorite.

389
00:29:31,580 --> 00:29:34,740
- It's made of purple rice. 
 - Mom?

390
00:29:37,739 --> 00:29:40,100
Why did you prepare so many dishes again?

391
00:29:40,100 --> 00:29:41,780
I have to hurry back in the afternoon.

392
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:43,259
Says who?

393
00:29:43,259 --> 00:29:44,639
You won't leave before dinner.

394
00:29:44,639 --> 00:29:46,140
It's not like you visit us often.

395
00:29:46,140 --> 00:29:49,280
You people are always on the go.

396
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:52,669
I have a date this afternoon. A mahjong date.

397
00:29:52,669 --> 00:29:55,699
You know what? How about you and dad come with us to our place?

398
00:29:55,699 --> 00:29:58,760
No! I get carsick.

399
00:29:58,760 --> 00:30:00,864
You and your mahjong all day long.

400
00:30:01,557 --> 00:30:06,200
You know what? It's up to my granddaughter when you can go.

401
00:30:09,340 --> 00:30:12,580
Jingjing, tell him.

402
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:17,459
Of course, we may leave only after dinner.

403
00:30:17,459 --> 00:30:20,259
See? I have to keep company to my grandparents.

404
00:30:20,259 --> 00:30:24,580
You are so old, yet you lack Jingjing's sensibilities.

405
00:30:24,580 --> 00:30:27,740
Jingjing. I'll take you to harvest bamboo shoots later.

406
00:30:27,740 --> 00:30:31,319
Your maternal grandma's bamboo shoots aren't as sweet as ours.

407
00:30:31,319 --> 00:30:33,547
We're not going back there.

408
00:30:35,939 --> 00:30:38,300
See how clever our granddaughter is.

409
00:30:38,300 --> 00:30:41,279
You've got us a bumper harvest.

410
00:30:42,119 --> 00:30:46,277
That's a lot of shoots. Okay, Jingjing.

411
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:50,179
Your sister has arrived at our house. They're waiting for us.

412
00:30:50,179 --> 00:30:52,219
See, your daughter harvested all of these.

413
00:30:52,219 --> 00:30:56,780
I'm thinking let's split them into fair portions so our guests won't scrap over them.

414
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:58,280
You're right.

415
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:02,140
You know what? Keep some for dad to dry.

416
00:31:02,140 --> 00:31:04,900
What? Drying the winter bamboo shoots?

417
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,219
It's not worth it.

418
00:31:06,219 --> 00:31:08,519
Take them all and distribute them.

419
00:31:08,519 --> 00:31:11,580
Tell them, my granddaughter harvested these shoots.

420
00:31:11,580 --> 00:31:12,860
To eat them is a blessing.

421
00:31:12,860 --> 00:31:14,019
Yeah.

422
00:31:14,019 --> 00:31:15,460
What are you doing here? Get down to work.

423
00:31:15,460 --> 00:31:16,640
Hurry up.

424
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:19,739
- Help us to pack these shoots. 
 - Yeah.

425
00:31:22,219 --> 00:31:26,319
Jingjing, you must eat well. Do you hear me?

426
00:31:26,319 --> 00:31:27,659
Get some good rest.

427
00:31:27,659 --> 00:31:29,327
It's so heavy.

428
00:31:30,300 --> 00:31:32,780
Drop by often when you're free.

429
00:31:35,900 --> 00:31:38,900
Take care, Grandma.

430
00:31:38,900 --> 00:31:41,660
- Dad, mom, we're going. 
 - Bye.

431
00:31:41,660 --> 00:31:44,258
- Go to bed early. 
 - Bye, Grandpa.

432
00:31:44,258 --> 00:31:45,940
- Remember to call us once you get there. 
 - Okay.

433
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:47,820
Hurry along now.

434
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:49,820
Easy there.

435
00:31:50,559 --> 00:31:52,140
Grandpa, Grandma, go in now. It's freezing out here.

436
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:53,240
Drive slowly.

437
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,900
- Mom, go in. 
 - Drive slowly.

438
00:31:54,900 --> 00:31:57,000
Okay.

439
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:09,980
 Jingjing, I'm back in Yixing. See you soon. 

440
00:32:09,980 --> 00:32:13,679
 I'm on my way back. Perhaps you can arrive a little later. 

441
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:31,940
It's your turn.

442
00:32:31,940 --> 00:32:33,238
Hurry up.

443
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,758
Nope.

444
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:36,660
A pair of jacks.

445
00:32:36,660 --> 00:32:38,319
Pair of two.

446
00:32:39,120 --> 00:32:40,100
Uncle is back.

447
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:42,119
Welcome back, Uncle!

448
00:32:42,119 --> 00:32:44,079
Look at me.

449
00:32:44,079 --> 00:32:46,277
What time is it now?

450
00:32:46,279 --> 00:32:47,440
How's the game?

451
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:49,140
Jingjing!

452
00:32:53,898 --> 00:32:57,478
What the hell? My MVP!

453
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:02,339
So nice!

454
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:06,119
It's really troublesome that my in-laws are in another place.

455
00:33:06,119 --> 00:33:07,480
Luckily, they're in Changzhou.

456
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:10,760
Otherwise, I wouldn't be able to hang out with you today.

457
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:13,539
That'd be a huge loss for me.

458
00:33:13,539 --> 00:33:16,360
Thanks a lot!

459
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:19,872
You're so nice, Jingjing.

460
00:33:19,872 --> 00:33:23,160
As a token of gratitude, let's go hang out somewhere. Drink's on me.

