00:33:45,599 --> 00:33:47,922
They come with private rooms.

471
00:33:47,922 --> 00:33:49,860
Okay then, let's go.

472
00:33:49,860 --> 00:33:51,739
Let's take a lot of photos, enough to post on WeChat Moments.

